6 stats

strength - max melee damage, strength saving throws
endurance - max health, endurance saving throws
agility - chance to dodge, agility saving throws
intelligence - max magic, spell damage, int saving throws
wisdom - magic regeneration rate per turn, spell damage, wis saving throws
luck - small impact on everything

2 ""bars""

health - beigns at 10
magic - begins at 0, unless player is magic-sensitive
